        <item>
            <title>新 Tesla Model 3 Performance 抵港　破百 3.1 秒 +  528KM 續航力</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/tesla-model-3-performance-press-release/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=tesla-model-3-performance-press-release</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/tesla-model-3-performance-press-release/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 05:59:53 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽車科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Insane Mode]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla Model 3]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Tesla Model 3 Performance]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[純電動車]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1231986</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>今日 Tesla 發布全新 Model 3 Performance 電動車，裏裏外外均有升級，0-100 km/h 加速更僅需 3.1 秒。以新「一換一」計劃計算，意向價為 $396,880 港幣。今日 Tesla 邀請了小編去看看 Tesla Model 3 Performance ，現在就帶大家欣賞這款全新熱門電動車。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232276" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09524-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09524-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09524.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232348" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09631-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09631-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09631.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>全新<span lang="EN-US"> Model 3 Performance </span>進行了內外部的升級，包括全新可調較自動適應減震系統、全新高效能 <span lang="EN-US">Mode<wbr />l 3 </span>摩打，<span lang="EN-US">0-100 km/h </span>加速只需<span lang="EN-US"> 3.1 </span>秒，最高時速可達 261 公里每小時，最高續航距離（WLTP）可達 528 公里。Model 3 Performance 配備帶有<span lang="EN-US"> Performance </span>標誌的通風<span lang="EN-US"> Sport </span>座椅、碳纖維尾翼和碳纖維內飾等，增強整體駕乘體驗，由 5 月 1 日起可於全線<span lang="EN-US"> Tesla </span>體驗中心參觀。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232277" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09543-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09543-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09543.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232343" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09628-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09628-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09628.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232349" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09629-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09629-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09629.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></h2><p style="text-align: center;">▲Performance 獨有標誌</p><h2>全新可調校自動適應減震系統 + Insane Mode</h2><p>Tesla Model 3 Performance 新增以軟件主導的可調校自動適應減震系統，能夠提升懸掛系統緩衝表現，有效減低路面對汽車的衝擊之餘，亦可保持車輛轉向靈活。Model 3 Performance 亦是第一款設有「Insane Mode」的 Model 3 系列電車。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232319" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09617-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09617-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09617.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲首次於 Model 3 加入 Insane Mode</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/tesla-price-reduce-2024-april/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Tesla 香港車價下調萬六元　Model 3 RWD 新一換一價 25.4 萬</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/29/bloomberg-said-tesla-baidu-may-work-together-for-tesla-fsd-in-china/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">彭博：Tesla 與百度將達成協議　協助 Tesla FSD 進入中國市場</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/29/elon-musk-visit-china-2024/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Elon Musk 訪華與李強會面   Tesla 全數通過中國汽車數據安全要求</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>Performance 高性能煞車制動、底盤</h2><p>根據廠方資料顯示，Model 3 Performance 配備更大的煞車碟、卡鉗及高性能剎車制動片，在任何速度都能夠提供強大制動力及一致的剎車體驗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232287" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09606-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09606-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09606.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Tesla Model 3 Performance 卡鉗</p><h2>鍛造 Performance 輪圈</h2><p>Model 3 Performance 標準配置新設計的 20 吋 Warp 版車輪，為駕駛者提供更清晰的轉向反饋，提升續航力及舒適度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232286" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09604-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09604-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09604.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲Model 3 Performance 標準配置 20 吋 Warp 版車輪</p><h2>通風 Sport 座椅</h2><p>全新設計的 Performance 前排座椅帶有 Performance 標誌，配備升級版座墊支撐包覆感更強，並且提供通風及暖感功能，為用家提供更一體化的乘坐體驗。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232325" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09601-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09601-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09601.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲前排座椅有 Performance 標誌</p><h2>碳纖維細節</h2><p>Model 3 Performance 加入了不少碳纖維元素，提升車輛「跑味」。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232328" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09625-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09625-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09625.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲碳纖維內飾</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232333" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09568-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09568-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09568.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲碳纖維尾翼</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/30/tesla-price-reduce-2024-april/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Tesla 香港車價下調萬六元　Model 3 RWD 新一換一價 25.4 萬</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/29/bloomberg-said-tesla-baidu-may-work-together-for-tesla-fsd-in-china/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">彭博：Tesla 與百度將達成協議　協助 Tesla FSD 進入中國市場</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/04/29/elon-musk-visit-china-2024/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Elon Musk 訪華與李強會面   Tesla 全數通過中國汽車數據安全要求</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>全新前後擾流設計</h2><p>為突顯 Model 3 Performance 的性能，Tesla 採用了不少跑車味濃的設計，例如全新的前後擾流及頭唇設計。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232331" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09587-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09587-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09587.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲全新頭唇</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232339" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09546-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09546-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09546.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232340" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09600-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09600-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09600.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲有效降低風阻的前擾流</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1232368" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09573-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09573-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/kan09573.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"> ▲後擾流設計</p><h2>Model 3 Performance Dual-Motor 規格</h2><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">加速（0-100 公里／小時）</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">3.1 秒</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">最高時速</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">261 公里／小時</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">續航距離（WLTP 標準）</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">528 公里</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">車輪</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">20&#8243; Warp 車輪</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">座位配置</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">5</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">尺寸</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;"><table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;"><tbody><tr><td style="width: 100%;">高度： 1,431 毫米</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 100%;">寬度： 1,933 毫米</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 100%;">長度： 4,724 毫米</td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">重量</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">1,854 公斤</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">容量</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">682 公升</td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">基本配置</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;"><ul><li style="text-align: left;">15.4 吋中央觸控螢幕及 8 吋後觸控式螢幕</li><li style="text-align: left;">可調節電動前排座椅</li><li style="text-align: left;">前排通風及暖感座椅；後排暖感座椅</li><li style="text-align: left;">自訂環境燈</li><li style="text-align: left;">3 個 USB 插口和手機無線充電（可為 2 部智能電話充電）</li><li style="text-align: left;">電熱軚盤</li><li style="text-align: left;">全車雙層隔音玻璃</li><li style="text-align: left;">專享網絡（30 天免費）</li></ul></td></tr><tr><td style="width: 39.1269%;">高級音響</td><td style="width: 60.8731%; text-align: center;">15 個喇叭和雙重低音喇叭<br />
